io.cui.tools.collect.CollectionBuilder

  • Packages that use CollectionBuilder 
    Package Description
    io.cui.tools.collect
    Provides a number of utilities in the context of Collections CollectionBuilder: Unified builder for building arbitrary Collections. CollectionLiterals: Provides literal-forms for creating populated collection instances.
